    s 6acaa "我还记得，男主注意到我似乎没那么喜欢文学。"

# game/topics.rpy:609
translate zho s_topics_art_lit_541f5225:

    # s "And, honestly? He was right."
    s "事实上呢？他是对的。"

# game/topics.rpy:610
