    # s "I just wish I could do more things with you that isn’t just sitting down for hours."
    s "我希望我能和你做更多的事情，而不仅仅是坐在这好几个小时。"

# game/topics.rpy:628
translate zho s_topics_art_lit_92c02cdb:

    # s 6aaca "Well, at the very least, I guess having something to read wouldn’t be so bad."
    s 6aaca "嗯，至少，在这里有些东西能读也不是那么糟。"

# game/topics.rpy:629
translate zho s_topics_art_lit_76c600de:

    # s 6aeba "I guess I should try to find something interesting online..."
    s 6aeba "我想我应该试着在网上找些好康的……"

# game/topics.rpy:631
translate zho s_topics_art_lit_46fcd71a:

    # s 6adbc "What’s that? 'Reddit'? Is it what I need now?"
    s 6adbc "这是什么？“Reddit”（国外著名贴吧网站）？这是我想要的吗？"

# game/topics.rpy:632
translate zho s_topics_art_lit_84d07664:

    # s 6adba "The club has a page there?"
    s 6adba "这里还有我们社团的网页？"

# game/topics.rpy:639
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_bbcd2087:

    # s "The more I learn about your world, the more surprised I get."
    s "随着我越了解你的世界，我越是感到惊讶。"

# game/topics.rpy:640
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_a0a7bdb5:

    # s "You still have a lot of silly conflicts despite how far you've come as a society..."
    s "不管你们为社会付出了多少，你们还是有很多愚蠢的冲突……"

# game/topics.rpy:641
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_7cacb097:

    # s "Why people can't just unite to resolve their common problems?"
    s "为什么人们就不能联合起来解决他们共同的问题？"

# game/topics.rpy:642
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_b4973e04:

    # s 6acab "Yes, they do on a limited scale, but usually only into several 'sub-groups' that still have different opinions and solutions."
    s 6acab "确实，他们也有视角局限性，不过即使把视野放大到“小组”比例，他们还是有不同的想法和方案。"

# game/topics.rpy:643
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_a29c84ae:

    # s "And these group often fight each other for power instead of deciding the problems."
    s "这些小组总是陷于权力的内斗，而不是专注于解决问题。"

# game/topics.rpy:644
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_03ba3eb0:

    # s "In addition, these groups often are so unstable that they can easily divide into smaller groups, hating each other."
    s "还有，这些组通常都不稳定，他们很容易分裂成更小的组，互相厌恶。"

# game/topics.rpy:645
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_2bd73d11:

    # s "They do it for reasons far more silly than the problems."
    s "他们这么做的理由比问题本身愚蠢得多。"

# game/topics.rpy:646
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_fc453c15:

    # s "You know, Monika told me something funny once, back from when she had just left the debating club."
    s "你知道的，莫妮卡有次告诉了我一些滑稽的事情，这得回到她刚退出辩论部的时候。"

# game/topics.rpy:647
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_437602a4:

    # s "'The strongest argument against democracy is a five minute conversation with the average person.'"
    s "“针对民主最有力的争论，就是与局外的普通人交流五分钟。”"

# game/topics.rpy:648
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_63289db0:

    # s "I think it's a pretty fair point to make, all things considered."
    s "从各方面考虑，我认为这个观点挺有道理。"

# game/topics.rpy:649
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_38f4e032:

    # s "While collaboration is great, somethimes you just need someone to step in so everyone can see the problem clearly."
    s "虽然合作确实是个不错的方法，但有时只需要有个第三方介入，每个人就能清楚地看到问题所在。"

# game/topics.rpy:650
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_fbe02933:

    # s "I think the literature club was a perfect example of it."
    s "我想这个文学部就是个完美的例子。"

# game/topics.rpy:651
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_cbd689a1:

    # s 6acaa "Remember the poem style arguments between Yuri and Natsuki?"
    s 6acaa "还记得优里和夏树之间关于写诗风格的争论吗？"

# game/topics.rpy:652
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_56dac916:

    # s "There wasn't really any problem between the two poems; both of them were just convinced that they were writing the 'correct' way."
    s "其实两种诗之间并不矛盾；她们只是坚信，她们各自写诗的方式是正确的。"

# game/topics.rpy:653
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_a6719016:

    # s "When I said they were both right, it wasn't a lie. Neither of them had done anything wrong, they just needed a third party to remind them that it wasn't a competition."
    s "我说她们都是对的，这不是在说谎。她们没有一个人做错了什么，只是需要一个第三方告诉她们这不是一场斗争。"

# game/topics.rpy:655
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_b2666ae3:

    # s 6abab "But when I was... gone, they didn't have someone who could help them see clearly, so they both went way too far."
    s 6abab "但当我……消失了，就没有一个人能帮助她们看清问题，所以她们就放飞自我了。"

# game/topics.rpy:656
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_76501cba:

    # s "Monika is a great debator, but she struggled when there was no easy way to decide how to handle the problem 'legally'."
    s "莫妮卡是个不错的辩手，但如果不能用简单的方法来决定怎么“合法”地处理这个问题，这个问题就很棘手了。"

# game/topics.rpy:657
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_dc5a151d:

    # s "...And she wanted to keep the game from crashing since I couldn't step in."
    s "……当我不能介入时，她想保持整个游戏正常不让它崩坏。"

# game/topics.rpy:658
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_986705e2:

    # s 6aaca "Anyway, the agrument didn't really change the club..."
    s 6aaca "总之，那些争论并没有真正改变这个社团……"

# game/topics.rpy:659
translate zho s_topics_society_conflicts_a0147a2d:

    # s 6abbb "But if Monika didn't take the two of you outside with her abilities, I hate to think what might have happened..."
    s 6abbb "但如果莫妮卡没有用她的能力带你从教室出来，我真不敢想象会发生什么……"

# game/topics.rpy:661
