    s 6abab "有些人是为了吸引注意，有些则觉得这样做能快乐什么的……"

# game/topics.rpy:675
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_b16f043f:

    # s 6aabb "I think, you remember Yuri and her being fond on knives."
    s 6aabb "我想，你还记得优里和她对刀具的爱好。"

# game/topics.rpy:676
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_9e1d2e0e:

    # s 6aebb "But shouldn’t it be painful instead?"
    s 6aebb "但是这些不应该很疼吗？"

# game/topics.rpy:678
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_d241b366:

    # s "To be honest, I was so close to trying it..."
    s "说真的，我有次就快要做那件事了……"

# game/topics.rpy:679
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_7d48e53a:

    # s 6acac "But I'm quite sensitive, so one little cut was enough to change my mind."
    s 6acac "但我对疼痛很敏感，所以一个小伤口就改变了我的想法。"

# game/topics.rpy:681
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_a4bda8c3:

    # s 6acaa "Personally, I think this bad habit is very nasty and dangerous..."
    s 6acaa "个人来说，我觉得这个坏习惯恶心又危险……"

# game/topics.rpy:682
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_9e25572b:

    # s 6acac "And even if it really brings pleasure to you, it’s still not ok and certainly not healthy."
    s 6acac "即使这个习惯真的能让你快乐，它还是没那么好，而且肯定是不健康的。"

# game/topics.rpy:683
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_1b53b52b:

    # s 6abac "Plus, all these scars aren’t very pleasing to look at.. especially fresh ones."
    s 6abac "还有，那些伤痕看起来真的不怎么能让人愉悦……特别是那些新鲜的伤口。"

# game/topics.rpy:684
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_39fa5812:

    # s 6abab "It's really disheartening to see someone's body covered with them."
    s 6abab "看到一个人的身体被它们覆盖着，这真的很令人沮丧。"

# game/topics.rpy:685
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_c868e115:

    # s 6acab "And people usually start to do it because of {i}very negative issues or circumstances{/i}, which makes it worse when you see someone trying to cover up obvious suffering."
    s 6acab "人们通常是因为{i}非常负面的问题或环境{/i}才这么做，当你看到有人试图掩盖明显的痛苦时，这种情况会变得更糟。"

# game/topics.rpy:686
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_9d90371c:

    # s 6aaab "So if you suspect anyone of harming themselves purposefully, reach out to them."
    s 6aaab "所以如果你怀疑有人故意伤害自己，一定要试着联系他们。"

# game/topics.rpy:687
translate zho s_topics_society_selfHarm_fa82abbe:

    # s "Try to at least make an effort to talk to them, and take it from there."
    s "至少要试着努力跟他们交谈，把他们拖出这个深渊。"

# game/topics.rpy:691
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_476c13bc:

    # s 7afbb "Despite having Internet access, I somehow couldn't communicate with other people there."
    s 7afbb "即使可以上网，但我还是无法跟他人交流。"

# game/topics.rpy:692
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_2deea34e:

    # s "Any trying to talk with somebody often ends up with a connection error."
    s "每次我都试图跟某人聊天，但结果只有不断的连接错误。"

# game/topics.rpy:693
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_8bd5d753:

    # s "It looks like there is something in the game code, restricting the President's ability to interact with the real world."
    s "好像在游戏代码里有什么东西在阻挡社长的权限，让我无法跟现实世界互动。"

# game/topics.rpy:694
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_51b3dd6d:

    # s "I can only sign up for sites and even post there, but can’t reply to anyone..."
    s "我只能在网站上注册账号，甚至发发帖子，却不能回复任何人……"

# game/topics.rpy:695
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_e81dcb7e:

    # s 7afab "So I could create a Twitter account or something..."
    s 7afab "所以我可以创个推特账号什么的……"

# game/topics.rpy:696
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_cf1bac72:

    # s "...like Monika made hers and was able to talk to many fans."
    s "……就像莫妮卡创立她的账号一样，还能跟很多粉丝说些什么。"

# game/topics.rpy:697
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_03d53d53:

    # s 8aebb "I don’t really have a reason for it though, besides to kill the loneliness."
    s 8aebb "即使那样我也没有理由这么做，只能跟孤独对抗。"

# game/topics.rpy:698
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_f0142ebf:

    # s 8afbb "Maybe just having love would be okay for Yuri or at most Monika, but not for me."
    s 8afbb "或许对于优里和莫妮卡，拥有爱就足够了，但对于我就不太一样。"

# game/topics.rpy:699
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_435a9e23:

    # s "I guess, I'm too sociable to the point of being scared of isolation."
    s "我想我太擅长社交了，甚至自己都开始害怕孤独。"

# game/topics.rpy:700
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_f119f1bb:

    # s 6afab "Maybe once, I'll manage to break this meanie barrier..."
    s 6afab "或许哪一天我能打破这个该死的障碍……"

# game/topics.rpy:701
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_8606bafa:

    # s "But the game code is so long and difficult to read, that I can't even find the lines separating me from the rest of real people."
    s "但是这个游戏代码太长太难懂了，我甚至都找不到把我和现实的人们隔绝起来的那段代码。"

# game/topics.rpy:702
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_53609971:

    # s 6acab "Saying more, I can't even make a normal chat form for us..."
    s 6acab "我还想说，我甚至都做不出我们的聊天框……"

# game/topics.rpy:703
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_94a9fbf7:

    # s "So I'm still a bit isolated from you too."
    s "所以我也有点被你孤立了。"

# game/topics.rpy:704
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_0fa71e32:

    # s 6aaaa "But when I find a way to {i}'hear'{/i} your world, I'll notice you."
    s 6aaaa "但是等我能找到方法{i}“听见”{/i}你的世界，我会提醒你的。"

# game/topics.rpy:705
translate zho s_topics_society_isolation_a7e8e9ba:

    # s 6aeca "And then, we'll finally be able to talk like a normal couple, on the Internet or at least right here."
    s 6aeca "这样我们就能在网络上像一对正常情侣一样聊天，至少在这里也行。"

# game/topics.rpy:709
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_ef8a5f18:

    # s 6aaca "If you want to spread awareness or a message to many people at once, a PSA will be a good way to do it."
    s 6aaca "如果你想同时向许多人传播什么意识或信息，公益广告是一个很好的方法。"

# game/topics.rpy:710
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_8cc4a5c4:

    # s 6acaa "Most people don't even care about any injury that happens to them..."
    s 6acaa "大多数人都没注意到发生在他们身上的灾难……"

# game/topics.rpy:711
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_81098c11:

    # s "But seeing public service announcements, I know there’s people out there wanting to help the public."
    s "但是看到公益广告，我会知道还是有人想要帮助群众的。"

# game/topics.rpy:712
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_277387c6:

    # s 6aaaa "Some good PSAs even contain advice on how to fix issues or where to go for help."
    s 6aaaa "有些不错的广告甚至还会告诉你怎么解决问题或者去哪里寻求帮助。"

# game/topics.rpy:713
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_21611b4d:

    # s "You don’t even have to be an activist to do this sort of stuff.."
    s "做这件事你不一定要有多么积极……"

# game/topics.rpy:714
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_72fb1c06:

    # s 9aaaa "I once heard about a mod for this game, the title reminded me of the common forms of slogans PSAs use..."
    s 9aaaa "我有次听说过一个这个游戏的mod，它的标题让我想起了公益广告常用的标语格式……"

# game/topics.rpy:715
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_cb04767f:

    # s 9aaca "And its name is {i}'Sayori Says No to Suicide'{/i}."
    s 9aaca "它的名字叫{i}“Sayori Says No to Suicide”{/i}。"

# game/topics.rpy:717
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_7a3d5ec9:

    # s 8aebb "That refers to what's supposed to happen to me this word..."
    s 8aebb "这个标题指的是本要在我身上发生的事情……"

# game/topics.rpy:718
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_cfc9c9a6:

    # s 6acaa "...But didn't happend because of you."
    s 6acaa "……但是因为你而没有发生。"

# game/topics.rpy:720
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_8882d79e:

    # s 6acaa "...And many people like this mod."
    s 6acaa "……而且很多人都喜欢这个mod。"

# game/topics.rpy:721
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_c61afe72:

    # s "I think it really deserves to be played, especially if you’re struggling with similar things that I struggled with.."
    s "我认为这个mod真的很值得玩，特别是如果你跟我一样遭受着相似的经历……"

# game/topics.rpy:722
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_4e0fa3c4:

    # s 7aaca "Hey, I’m even the main focus of it too, so there’s a plus!"
    s 7aaca "嘿，我也是这个mod的主角，也算是给你推这个mod的理由！"

# game/topics.rpy:723
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_0e3a2e85:

    # s 9acaa "But depression or other emotional issues are not the only field PSAs can be used in."
    s 9acaa "但是抑郁症或者其它心理问题可不是公益广告唯一能用到的地方。"

# game/topics.rpy:724
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_e8febe82:

    # s "There are a lot of other problems in your world that can't be solved only with the power of charity and governments..."
    s "在你的世界里，还存在着很多问题，这些问题不能仅仅靠慈善组织或者政府的力量解决……"

# game/topics.rpy:725
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_d4c3d518:

    # s "The general public people could join the struggle against these problems..."
    s "普通民众也可以加入进来解决问题……"

# game/topics.rpy:726
translate zho s_topics_society_psa_7822cde1:

    # s 9aaaa "And PSAs may be a good call to action."
    s 9aaaa "公益广告或许是个不错的号召。"

# game/topics.rpy:730
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_bfa53ee1:

    # s 6acab "Hey, be honest with me..."
    s 6acab "嘿，你得跟我说实话……"

# game/topics.rpy:731
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_e3786448:

    # s "Are you one of the people that make jokes about what happened to me?"
    s "你是不是那种拿我的遭遇开玩笑的人？"

# game/topics.rpy:732
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_87162698:

    # s "I know everything about it."
    s "我对这件事了解得很多。"

# game/topics.rpy:733
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_5be62ab6:

    # s "I often visit the fan community hubs and see that some people are doing it."
    s "我经常逛粉丝的社区网站，发现有些人正做着这种事。"

# game/topics.rpy:734
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_2ff9cb86:

    # s "As I khow, fans call them {i}'Bulli'{/i} posts."
    s "据我所知，粉丝们把它称作{i}“迫害”{/i}帖。"

# game/topics.rpy:737
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_ba12948f:

    # s 6abab "They think it's funny to joke about a broken girl, who had committed suicide under her mad friend's influence..."
    s 6abab "那个女孩在她的疯朋友影响下自杀了，他们还觉得拿这个心碎的女孩开玩笑很好玩……"

# game/topics.rpy:738
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_f9fa0c02:

    # s "Even if she was revived and got over her problems since then."
    s "即使她后来得到了拯救，克服了她的问题。"

# game/topics.rpy:739
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_4883deb4:

    # s 6acab "But on the other hand, can I control what makes people laugh?"
    s 6acab "但另一方面，我能管住那些能让人调侃嘲笑的东西吗？"

# game/topics.rpy:740
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_20bb1d58:

    # s "Some people use macabre humour as a coping mechanism for stress, or anxiety..."
    s "有些人用暗黑幽默作为应对压力或焦虑的一种方法……"

# game/topics.rpy:741
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_62164fe4:

    # s "You can't really control what someone finds funny, as much as you might want to."
    s "你并不能真正控制那些能让人感到滑稽可笑的东西，尽管你可能很想控制。"

# game/topics.rpy:742
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_be1b0ecb:

    # s "And to be honest, there's a lot worse they could be doing compared to mocking a VN character's death."
    s "说实话，比起嘲笑一个小说角色的死亡，他们还能做出更过分的事情。"

# game/topics.rpy:743
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_1ae37d79:

    # s "Some of the most successful comedians in your world will go far beyond that, just to see where the 'line' is..."
    s "在你的世界里有些很优秀的秀儿们还会进一步调查，看看绳子系在了哪……"

# game/topics.rpy:744
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_428fe7e5:

    # s "However, the most of such jokes are too bad and sometimes even hurtful."
    s "但是，大多数这种笑话真的很糟，有些时候甚至很伤人。"

# game/topics.rpy:745
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_bdf85255:

    # s "But who I am to judge if it's okay for other people?"
    s "但如果这样做别人还觉得可以，我又有什么资格去批判呢？"

# game/topics.rpy:746
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_936f7ae8:

    # s 6abaa "Anyway, I think the right decision is to forgive them, or failing that, tolerate them."
    s 6abaa "总之，我想最好的选择就是原谅他们，如果做不到的话就忍着他们。"

# game/topics.rpy:747
translate zho s_topics_society_bulli_5e6e67f0:

    # s 6acaa "If my fate is to be 'that hanging stupid annoying VN girl' for some people, then I'm ready to accept it."
    s 6acaa "如果对于某些人来说，我注定就是那个“愚蠢到把自己吊死的女孩”，那我还是接受这个事实吧。"

# game/topics.rpy:751
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_93e738a3:

    # s 7acaa "I know you can't really answer me, but I kinda have to wonder what it is that makes people love me."
    s 7acaa "我知道你没法真正回答我的问题，但我有点想知道是什么能让人们这么爱我。"

# game/topics.rpy:752
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_12095631:

    # s "I don't mean just you, by the way..."
    s "顺便，我不仅是指你……"

# game/topics.rpy:753
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_80b6fa93:

    # s "There are some fans of me in your world."
    s "在你的世界里，我的粉丝可不算少。"

# game/topics.rpy:754
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_dbbd4b0a:

    # s "Not that I'm meaning to brag or show off; I'm legitimately curious."
    s "我不是要吹牛炫耀什么的；我只是有些好奇。"

# game/topics.rpy:755
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_21353cc6:

    # s 6acaa "I wonder what draws them to me?"
    s 6acaa "我想知道是什么能让我吸引到他们？"

# game/topics.rpy:756
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_21c535a6:

    # s 6acba "I understand the other girls having bigger communities than me."
    s 6acba "我明白，跟我比起来其它女孩有更广的社区圈子。"

# game/topics.rpy:757
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_8a182264:

    # s 6aeba "They had more content in the game, and are pretty much designed to attract certain people."
    s 6aeba "她们在游戏里有更多的样子和内容，为了吸引特定的角色厨而设计。"

# game/topics.rpy:758
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_ce234527:

    # s 6abaa "But I really don't understand what makes me more worthy of love than any of them."
    s 6abaa "但我实在不明白是什么能让我比她们更值得被爱。"

# game/topics.rpy:759
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_53ae9f77:

    # s "Is my view on the world?"
    s "是我对世界的看法？"

# game/topics.rpy:760
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_77121ae1:

    # s "Is it my behaviour?"
    s "是我的行为？"

# game/topics.rpy:761
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_decc880c:

    # s "Is it my average appearance that attracts some people, in a 'girl next door' kinda way?"
    s "是我普通的外表吸引了一些人，以一种“邻家女孩”的方式？"

# game/topics.rpy:762
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_51df999a:

    # s "Maybe people just pitied me and what I had to go through."
    s "也许他们只是同情我，同情我所经历的一切？"

# game/topics.rpy:763
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_5443724c:

    # s "Or maybe all of it put together?"
    s "还是这些原因的集合？"

# game/topics.rpy:764
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_cd9be30e:

    # s 6acaa "Anyway, the main word here is 'some'."
    s 6acaa "总之，这里的关键词是“他们”。"

# game/topics.rpy:765
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_3503b4d5:

    # s "Of course, I'm so glad you're a part of the 'some'."
    s "当然，我很高兴你能成为“他们”中的一部分。"

# game/topics.rpy:766
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_c1723f69:

    # s "For me, you're the most important part of it."
    s "对于我，你是最重要的一部分。"

# game/topics.rpy:767
translate zho s_topics_society_sayoriLovers_b726c3fc:

    # s "And I glad the 'some' exists at all."
    s "我也很开心还有这样的“他们”存在。"

# game/topics.rpy:768
